c=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 著細一個碼就穿唔過小腿，大一個就塞到成隻手入褲到"},{"pid":"aa227afc3fefa9fe1987114c7ff8c37f68efea4b","tid":381871,"uid":10268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T11:13:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果小腿太粗，但係係肌肉大舊咁點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好難買褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 著細一個碼就穿唔過小腿，大一個就塞到成隻手入褲到</blockquote><br />\n屌我都係 <br />\n中學果陣練田徑練到小腿勁粗 成日比人笑<br />\n一著窄腳褲個小腿形就出哂黎 勁樣衰 <br />\n想知點減走小腿啲肌肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6c5895ca19605a914c4a5121cccfda67f9ec75c","tid":381871,"uid":130663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T12:33:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>負重單腳踩高一級仔「gut」高腳</blockquote><br />\n呢個做左一個月 但感覺越做越大</blockquote><br />\n做得快唔快？<br />\n<br />\n我都有做相同訓練 不過盡力上落快<br />\n越做個小腿越細+高</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪做輕磅多下數會好啲 太重反而越操脹<br />\n以前打開波 舊肌肉真係細同高 <br />\n而家又大又dur<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9660f8d1a0fa34e89cc596574fd80d37dac6a1bb","tid":381871,"uid":78046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T13:06:47.000Z","msg":"練大啲大腳 小腳想對就細"},{"pid":"88675b4464b1fce4c86c2b0136ce199707f8b3a8","tid":381871,"uid":78046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T13:06:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>練大啲大腳 小腳想對就細</blockquote><br />\n腿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"032aa4f646ae25bfd28981a75b8f8f051d0c5c72","tid":381871,"uid":38440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T13:07:37.000Z","msg":"長跑"},{"pid":"395d338448604554258c0d135f72415a35933893","tid":381871,"uid":34927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T13:10:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>練大啲大腳 小腳想對就細</blockquote><br />\n腿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你改完都係錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7f63850a6b7efd5cd9ea5b9ac667c0af67f7511","tid":381871,"uid":57643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T13:14:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>練大啲大腳 小腳想對就細</blockquote><br />\n腿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你改完都係錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n練大d對腳，小腿相對就細？"},{"pid":"cb2c7a41cf983e5a2490415a998a88df9359cd75","tid":381871,"uid":59046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T13:49:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>負重單腳踩高一級仔「gut」高腳</blockquote><br />\n呢個做左一個月 但感覺越做越大</blockquote><br />\n做得快唔快？<br />\n<br />\n我都有做相同訓練 不過盡力上落快<br />\n越做個小腿越細+高</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪做輕磅多下數會好啲 太重反而越操脹<br />\n以前打開波 舊肌肉真係細同高 <br />\n而家又大又dur<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我自己覺得係 <br />\n做7-8成重12-15下快嘅 做5set<br />\n<br />\n但做得快就容易一下唔專心就扭傷"},{"pid":"75b640a94bec85c358439a42beb189efe4dd8d63","tid":381871,"uid":141283,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T15:48:47.000Z","msg":"其實係咪遺傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲人隻腳就算點練 都會保留到個形<br />\n我老豆係梨形腳<br />\n我隻腳同佢差唔多形 加上又矮 搞到著短褲都好核突 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"545c0bd6a181133f1858c284440ddd068f583fda","tid":381871,"uid":130663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T15:56:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實係咪遺傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲人隻腳就算點練 都會保留到個形<br />\n我老豆係梨形腳<br />\n我隻腳同佢差唔多形 加上又矮 搞到著短褲都好核突 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n180男神都矮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2ad02f6ff858a7af24394ffea625d3e0856c445","tid":381871,"uid":69873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T20:02:36.000Z","msg":"同問<br />\n我直頭係成舊肥肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a26f2ee24e536df7cf3c163b3e3c22ca8b2edcc","tid":381871,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T22:16:21.000Z","msg":"瞓覺搵啲運動繃帶扎住小腿 兩三個月自然會幼"}]}